<subSubSection id="C311B0F9CA2BFFD8EEBDFE2F43C1FDFE" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB4E372CA2BFFD8EEBDFE2F43C1FDFE" pageId="50" pageNumber="495">
Morphologically and ecologically nearest to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0B98F1CA2BFFD8EC86FE2F4509FE6E" authority="Legrand, 1982" authorityName="Legrand" authorityYear="1982" box="[676,1036,450,477]" class="Insecta" family="Coenagrionidae" genus="Aciagrion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="balachowskyi">
