(Sjöstedt, 
<number id="3DC3F155CA2BFFD8EEBDFDE141DCFD95" box="[159,217,524,551]" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" value="1909.0">1909</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
and treated as a distinct species on account of its unique male appendages by Dijkstra &amp; Clausnitzer (
<number id="3DC3F155CA2BFFD8EC5BFDDF43B2FDFE" box="[633,695,562,588]" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" value="2014.0">2014</number>
).
</paragraph>
